Package org.dspace.xmlworkflow.state.actions.processingaction

Class Summary
AcceptEditRejectAction Processing class of an action that allows users to edit/accept/reject a workflow item
FinalEditAction Processing class of an action that allows users to accept/reject a workflow item
ProcessingAction A class that that extends the action to support the common isAuthorized method
ReviewAction Processing class of an accept/reject action
ScoreEvaluationAction Processing class for the score evaluation action This action will allow multiple users to rate a certain item if the mean of this score is higher then the minimum score the item will be sent to the next action/step else it will be rejected
ScoreReviewAction This action will allow multiple users to rate a certain item if the mean of this score is higher then the minimum score the item will be sent to the next action/step else it will be rejected
SelectReviewerAction Processing class for an action where an assigned user can assign another user to review the item
SingleUserReviewAction Processing class of an action where a single user has been assigned and he can either accept/reject the workflow item or reject the task
